# Design system

Dark technical creative tool — follow **`.impeccable.md`**.

| Area | Rule |
| --- | --- |
| **Density** | Comfortable spacing for prose/dialogs/help; compact for inspectors/parameters; one dense region inside a calm frame beats all-dense |
| **Color** | Tokens from `src/styles/*.css`; accents mean state (selection, primary, animated/connected — see `tokens-node-editor.css`), not decoration |
| **Motion** | Subtle polish; **`prefers-reduced-motion`** always |
| **Icons** | Phosphor-aligned; stroke from icon tokens |
| **Copy** | Short, supportive, non-judgmental; skip corporate fluff and forced “playful” |

**Ship checklist:** primitives from `src/lib/components/ui/` • adaptive density • tokens only (+ justified new ones) • reduced motion • clear focus/hover/disabled states
